---
<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <div class="hero-layout fade-in">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Sudhakar Chaulagain</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Security engineer & developer</p>
      <p class="bio">
        CS junior at Southeastern Louisiana University. I build security tools, compete in national Hackathons, CTFs, and write code that's harder to break. Currently looking for Summer 2026 internships.
      </p>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://github.com/Sudhakar-exe" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/sudhakarchaulagain" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="mailto:sudhakar.chaulagain@selu.edu">Email</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo fade-in d2">
      <img src="/images/sudhakar.jpeg" alt="Sudhakar Chaulagain" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero { padding-top: 6rem; padding-bottom: 5rem; border-top: none !important; }
  .hero-layout {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  .hero-text { max-width: 580px; }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .subtitle {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .bio {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .links a {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .links a:hover { border-color: var(--text); opacity: 1; }
  .hero-photo { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .hero-photo img {
    width: 200px;
    height: 245px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 3px;
    filter: grayscale(15%);
    transition: filter 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .hero-photo img:hover {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .hero-layout { flex-direction: column-reverse; gap: 2rem; }
    .hero-photo img { width: 120px; height: 150px; }
  }
</style>